<br>
Post your strategy here: ****<br>
<br>
-Desteven<br>
58th Knight of Tunare <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uwollyen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wollyen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/22/01 6:27:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> since you're a pally, i'll help ya =)<br>
<br>
Get 2 groups.<br>
<br>
Attack and kill Peffin.<br>
<br>
Don't use any damage shields, dont attack any giants.<br>
<br>
That's it...simple aint it?  Don't worry about anything tricky, its a speed kill... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulewterpitt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LEWTERPITT</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.socal.rr.com/moshpitt/shadowdevils/images/pics/inmybelly-.gif width=50 height=30" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/22/01 11:26:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> Tash aggros. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprodigious.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prodigious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/23/01 10:42:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> bring like 10 people, mainly for killing the 3 elites that run. if you can find someone to kite these away you don't need more than 1 person (kiter)<br>
<br>
for peffin, bring some high lvl wizards and lure nuke her down.....run in quick and loot. lures landed pretty well just a few days ago. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upieksykenderkin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pieksy Kenderkin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/23/01 11:28:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> Bring 1 group, including 2 clerics.<br>
<br>
Send in maintank, clerics CHing right away. All 5 giants will aggro on clerics. Send in rest of melee. Kill, loot, /dance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhieya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hieya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/23/01 11:42:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> bring 1 druid or wizzy with aoe snare, a cleric, and a melee. have him aoe snare all the static giants at the camp fire to get aggro. then just walk in the middle of them and kill peffin. the giants will be so intent on kilking the druid who aoe snared them theyll ignore everything else and since they cant move from the point they spawned at, they cant kill the druid whos holding their aggro.<br>
<br>
other thing you can do is bring someone who has a breezeboots frigid gnasher, and just blast all the giants away from peffin up against the back wall. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ughary.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ghary</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/24/01 11:35:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> The easiest way is to bring one group.  I've done in probably 6 times already this way.  You will need a cleric and a druid/ranger for the fight.<br>
<br>
Have the group stand outside the fort.  Have the guy doing it hand in the note to peffin to spawn the giants.  Get someone with sow to agro the three elites that are outside the hut and kite them around.  Pick them off one by one and kill them.<br>
<br>
Then run to behind the fire where peffin is.  Have your druid or ranger harmony all the giants.  Then kill peffin.  If the druid/ranger did their job none will agro you and it will be cake. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usslithissik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sslithissik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/24/01 12:49:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> two rangers, spawn peffin, kite giants, voiddance yer ass in loot head, out, bang bang <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucily.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cily</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/25/01 2:27:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> yea... except you cant kite the giants.<br>
<br>
&quot;easiest&quot; way is to have a lvl 60 wizard just solo peffin for you.<br>
<br>
But there are dozens of other options of course.<br>
<br>
Cily <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ualuerin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aluerin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/25/01 6:32:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> Did it with 5 people last week, only needed 3 however.  I turned in note, ran out of the room real fast and didn't aggro the guys inside.  Had a wizard cast AE snare on the giants around the fire about 5 times, then he sat down just out of melee range.  Then me, a warrior, a wizard and a monk killed Peffin while a cleric healed a little and the wizard kept the Giants aggroed on him.  Then I looted and we just walked out. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uviken.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Viken</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/15/01 7:24:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3333.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Peffin Strategy...</span><hr size=1> Ingrediants:<br>
1 Ranger with Trueshot<br>
1 Monk<br>
1 Cleric<br>
1 Wizard with Lure<br>
<br>
Strat:<br>
1. Kill the 2 giants at the gate<br>
2. Kill the captain<br>
3. Kill the giant near the fire<br>
4. Kill the 2 giants in the house blocking Peffin<br>
5. Monk pulls Peffin to the gate and FD<br>
6. Hand in the note<br>
7. Ranger /trueshot Peffin pushing her on top of the logs and dropping her behind them. After trueshot wears off Peffin should be close to 50% health. Keep shooting arrows until she drops down behind the logs.<br>
8. Once she falls behind the log fire have the Wizard burn her down.<br>
9. Go in and loot. Corpse will be far away enough from the giants that you never have to worry about getting hit by giants.<br>
<br>
This is very trivial after you've seen it done once. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
